      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning, showroom-quality beauty! This car is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving just as it did on day one. It has been meticulously preserved and cared for, offering a truly flawless experience for its next owner. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is essentially brand new!",
