    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six powerplant, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900-RPM redline. The engine benefits from a recent valve adjustment and a comprehensive Double-VANOS refresh to ensure optimal cam timing. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a mechanical limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to address the chassis's known torsional fatigue points. The suspension features a refreshed multi-link rear setup and MacPherson struts with Bilstein dampers, preserving the communicative steering and neutral handling balance this platform is known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance and throttle response.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
