    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. Finished in a stunning Deep Metallic Blue, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only the typical light road peppering on the front bumper expected from careful highway use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine charcoal leather interior with zero tears or bolster wear. Every feature, from the heated power seats to the premium surround-sound system and panoramic sunroof, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has been strictly serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were recently serviced with new pads and rotors. It sits on a set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a non-smoker, garage-kept vehicle that needs nothing but a new owner. Complete service records are available for review to ensure total peace of mind.",
      "price": 31500.0,
